Xiao Ci saved your life

18
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:13.566
We have to help her

19
00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:14.566
That child has suffered a lot

20
00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:19.133
Don’t bully her, okay?

21
00:01:19.166 --> 00:01:21.233
Got it

22
00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:23.033
